{
  "stem": "13673.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I still wonder-- we will wonder why Hitler didn't invade England, you know, but thank god he didn't.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so I could no longer stay there as a boarder.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Miss Callis, the headmistress, arranged for me to-- to live with her brother and his family in what's called the Midlands of England, in a-- in a little town called Wellingborough.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She took me there and-- by train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did everything by train or bus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very strict, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but kind, in their way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I was with them for about three and 1/2 years, it turned out, and thought of myself as their-- as their, not their daughter exactly, but part of their family.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had a daughter who had been going to my Lonsdale School, because that was her aunt's school, after all.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But she was older than I and she-- she left before I did,  and she-- she joined one of the armed services in England.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had a son.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They also took in a-- the son was in the navy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They also took in a ref-- a-- an evacuee from London.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were-- there was a different, a fine distinction, between an evacuee and a refugee.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was the refugee.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was the evacuee.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the evacuee ca-- was sent out of London because of the bombing-- the Blitz that started pretty soon after, to go.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But her parents were still in London, and she could go back anytime she wanted to, and many did.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So their parents knew where they were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They could visit them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They could see each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I, as a refugee, had-- had to leave my country and learn a new language and not see my parents.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
